<paragraph blockId="30.[189,1399,506,532]" box="[189,1399,506,532]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
Geographic distributions of the 
<taxonomicName box="[557,726,506,532]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Trichomyrmex" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
